headline: Duke Energy reports over 18,000 outages in Carolinas, with more expected as ice threatens trees and power lines
summary: Winter Storm Fern continues to deliver freezing rain and sleet across the Carolinas – bringing down trees, limbs and power lines and causing scattered outages.
